name: Coloring Book: Roboto 6659 Halloween
description:
Created for the Draw Roboto Competition. This character is the first design of a coloring book series. In this series I will take avatar of my own or provided by other community members to draft coloring book pages. Maybe we make a collective book? :D 

Share how you color in the roboto! @velcrafting on twitter!
Extra special thanks to @MelisaMimosa420 for providing Roboto 6659
